OL,3,CWarwick Hospital saves money and
OL,4,C'improves patient care' by using new
OL,5,Capp
OL,7,FA new app which helps healthcare staff
OL,8,Fdecide where best to treat people has
OL,9,Fimproved care for elderly patients and
OL,10,Fsaved money, according to Warwick
OL,11,FHospital.
OL,13,FConsultant Connect works by connecting
OL,14,Fparamedics and GPs directly to a
OL,15,Fhospital consultant who assesses the
OL,16,Fneeds of the frail patients over 75.
OL,18,FA decision is then made about whether
OL,19,Fthat person needs to be brought into
OL,20,Fhospital, or if they can be treated
OL,21,Fbetter in the community.
