OL,3,CWarwick Hospital saves money and
OL,4,C'improves patient care' by using new
OL,5,Capp
OL,7,FIn the last year the app has been used
OL,8,Fapproximately 1400 times, and in
OL,9,Faround half of those cases, people
OL,10,Fhave been treated at home instead of
OL,11,Fthe hospital.
OL,13,FParamedic Claire Sweet says the app is
OL,14,Fbeneficial for many patients, adding:
OL,15,F"it is important to keep a patient in
OL,16,Ftheir own environment, it stops muscle
OL,17,Fwastage as if you end up in hospital
OL,18,Fthen it is a prolonged amount of time,
OL,19,Fpossibly in a bed, and if you are able
OL,20,Fto be treated at home it is a lot
OL,21,Fnicer and a lot easier".
