OL,3,CWarwick Hospital saves money and
OL,4,C'improves patient care' by using new
OL,5,Capp
OL,7,FThe app is used instead of a phone
OL,8,Fcall because it allows those accessing
OL,9,Fit to see patient records.
OL,11,FIt means patients only have to call
OL,12,Fone number to get through to a
OL,13,Fconsultant and the calls are recorded
OL,14,Fso the hospital can keep records.
OL,16,FWarwick Hospital says that by treating
OL,17,Fpeople in the community, instead of in
OL,18,Fhospital, they have been able to close
OL,19,Fa surge ward, resulting in savings of
OL,20,Fmore than #1.5 million in temporary
OL,21,Fstaffing costs.
